data.description:
Don't overlook this stunning Ranch home located in the SE Polk School District! Boasting over 2,800 square feet of finished space, you'll have ample room for all your needs. The main level offers an inviting open floor plan, complemented by a spacious deck off the living room, providing a delightful backyard view. The generously sized master bedroom features a large walk-in closet and a bathroom with a double vanity and a spacious soaking tub. The kitchen is well-appointed with abundant cabinet space, and all appliances are included. You'll adore the living room with its cozy fireplace and view of the backyard. Another large bedroom, bathroom, laundry room, and an office space with French doors complete the main level.
Heading downstairs, you'll discover plenty of storage space, two more generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an additional spacious living area that opens up to the spacious park-like yard. Recent updates include new gutters and windows in 2019, a new roof and garage doors in 2020, new flooring in the basement, and a newer HVAC system. Don't miss the opportunity to schedule a showing before this gem is gone!
